      "side": 1,
      "message": "This description doesn\u0027t seem accurate, it is my understanding that this is also the pool on which the connection forwarders will be forwarded on. This approach requires 3 threads per connection which may be hard to manage properly. Imagine a limited pool being supplied here. Even if it has a limit which is a multiple of 3, it can potentially accept new connections so fast that it does not leave enough threads for the forward() calls.",
      "revId": "00a6511e7d6d0ed1556dea3f0176049760761260",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
    },
